{"tid":2302695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【香港未來？】感恩節：中國哈工大宿管員派糖果遭學生批評“過洋節”，校方支持舉報","createTime":"2020-11-27T10:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:33:15.000Z","uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8db803113719b28d52cf7122729184bebe5a1c07","tid":2302695,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-55099127?at_custom3=BBC+Chinese&amp;at_custom4=EF2BC846-3090-11EB-8906-767D4D484DA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fchinese-news-55099127%3Fat_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%26at_custom4%3DEF2BC846-3090-11EB-8906-767D4D484DA4&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpPuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=ba7a321e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fchinese-news-55099127%3Fat_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%26at_custom4%3DEF2BC846-3090-11EB-8906-767D4D484DA4&h=4d6f93ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-55099127?at_custom3=BBC+Chinese&amp;at_custom4=EF2BC846-3090-11EB-8906-767D4D484DA4</a><br />\n<br />\n在中國，過不過來自西方的節日一直是一個火藥味十足的話題。<br />\n<br />\n最近，一名哈爾濱工業大學學生的言論再次點燃了火藥桶。他威脅將舉報一名宿舍管理員，因為後者打算在感恩節向學生們贈送糖果。<br />\n<br />\n這名就讀於該校的學生認為，這是&ldquo;宣傳西方節日&rdquo;，&ldquo;非常不妥&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此事曝光後，該學生遭到了大量網友的抨擊。很多網友認為他在&ldquo;上綱上線&rdquo;、&ldquo;小題大做&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n但哈工大在周五（11月27日）作出回應，對該學生的行為表示肯定。稱學校&ldquo;不提倡有宗教色彩的'洋節'進校園，堅決禁止宗教活動進校園。 &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/7FEA/production/_115664723_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F7FEA%2Fproduction%2F_115664723_1.jpg&h=b68519fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35edcb5d599f8eab1aa99909c338e6de25e450fc","tid":2302695,"uid":164374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8db803113719b28d52cf7122729184bebe5a1c07","tid":2302695,"uid":290118,